      public static int getRandom​(int min, int max)

    • removeIndex

      public static int[] removeIndex​(int[] numbers, int index)
      Removes an index from array and returns it Method is given an array and an index. When it gets to the index, it removes it's value and continues. New array will be one shorten than the original.
      Parameters:
      numbers - the original array
      index - index to remove
      Returns:
      new array with the index removed
